{"tid":403222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[姐姐有冇見到我張成績表]兩兒童2分鐘內接連墜樓過路女子險被砸傷","createTime":"2017-09-17T04:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T12:00:40.000Z","uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"967776e03bfa11d68b5c750e41564bc95d1f5680","tid":403222,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"9月15日，廣東東莞發生一起兩兒童接連墜樓的悲劇事件，監控顯示：一名紅衣女子正在路邊行走，此時一名兒童直接從空中墜落，並險些將紅衣女子砸中，紅衣女子被嚇到，趕緊後退。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.utuku.china.com/uploadimg/news/20170916/1df0ea20-f861-4dc2-bd02-4defd5aacd12.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.utuku.china.com%2Fuploadimg%2Fnews%2F20170916%2F1df0ea20-f861-4dc2-bd02-4defd5aacd12.gif&h=598742be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就在路人圍觀之時，又有一名孩子出現在窗口，一名男子急忙阻止，不料孩子也墜落。路人衝上前去，接住無果，孩子重摔在地，目前兩名孩子已送醫治療。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img2.utuku.china.com/358x0/news/20170916/ce7acc9a-21a7-448c-a14c-892896403827.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.utuku.china.com%2F358x0%2Fnews%2F20170916%2Fce7acc9a-21a7-448c-a14c-892896403827.png&h=c434c0e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7e5a7486f33e3e19ae2fc3b63e85b3c54885cf","tid":403222,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:37:39.000Z","msg":"i believe i can fly"},{"pid":"6f19d636bedcf051c16fa90711ed9fed3a468fce","tid":403222,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ddc58dba328a66847a237ce12eb512bcc1be4c5","tid":403222,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"1999，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f474c65137f5d668f32fa43c43a8ef78ed99a8","tid":403222,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq